, \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"the faith\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not really want to weigh in on the Olympics opening ceremony publicly because I always risk becoming a headline,\\\" she said in an Instagram post on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2727, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1738783242163309e-29, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"a headline\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it felt too important not to.\\\"\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Games have always brought me so much joy.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"so much joy\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best of the best athletes in the world competing for the title,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best athletes\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So to watch such an incredible and wonderful event that's going to take place over the next two weeks and see the opening ceremonies completely blaspheme and mock the Christian faith with their interpretations of the Last Supper was disgusting.\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3097, \"end\": 3106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc